scene.message:
Maki: This scenery... I feel{nl}
like I've seen it somewhere{nl}
before.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: {ctl0f:1}...{nl}
Is your weapon ready?{waitkey}This time I won't let him{nl}
slip away!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: We're almost there...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Soon we'll beat Kandori and{nl}
put the town back to normal...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: This time we'll beat{nl}
Kandori and set the town{nl}
right again!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: ...{wait_fr:32}I wish I had a{nl}
researcher all to myself,{nl}
too.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Those guys are the{nl}
worst! All they think about{nl}
is their own research!{waitkey}{ret}

Scientist: Curse Kandori!{waitkey}{nl}
Keeping himself safe while he{nl}
leaves us as demon prey, is{nl}
that his plan?!{waitkey}{ret}

Scientist: I don't see Dr.{nl}
Nicolai anywhere...{waitkey}{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Just when I thought he was up{nl}
to something on the sly,{waitkey}he'd wormed his way into{nl}
Kandori's good graces!{waitkey}{ret}

Scientist: At this rate, my{nl}
precious experiment data will{nl}
be ruined! Ahh, my important{nl}
research...!{waitkey}{ret}
